dct_title_s: Plan no. 1 of lots of Silver Bay,Township of Dover, Ocean County, New Jersey
dct_description_sm: The map is a negative photostat that shows property lots in the Silver Bay area between Main Street and Barnegat Bay and Silver Bay Harbor. It has two attached enlargements stapled.
Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
Handwritten inscription in lower right corner states Map File 112-1A.
Dover Township, Ocean County changed its name to Toms River in 2006.
